</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l7">
<add><ab facs="#facs_110_r1l1">habt </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd erklagt hab </del> / Biten vvir euch
                                <expan>fleiſſıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ Jr
                                <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l8">
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein
                        ſchulde <del rend="strikethrough">noch
                            <expan>onvercʒieh<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> richten vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l9">becʒalen <del rend="strikethrough">wol </del> vnd Jn
