<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_110_r2l12">ııj̃ poſt <expan>Ephy<ex>pha</ex><hi rend="sup">nie</hi></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nj</expan> Anno etc xv<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_110" id="55r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen vom Eglofstein czum Rotemberg gesessen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Hans, uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Moricz Auracher,
                        unser <add>diener</add>, wie ir im etwievil schuldig bleibt, das <add>ir im
                            lang zeit verczogen</add>
<add>habt;</add> biten wir euch <expan>fleissiklich<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz
                        ir <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein
                        schulde richten und beczalen und in darümb unklaghaft
                            <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, als etc. Das wöllen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii post <expan>ephy<ex>pha</ex><hi rend="sup">nie</hi></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan> anno etc. xv<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
